      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.hIhgdXnqGHBm0A64]{Envoy Improvisation}</p>\n<p>@Icon[type:mind-affecting] @Icon[type:sense-dependent]</p>\n<p>As a standard action, you can encourage a single ally within 60 feet to focus on the danger at hand. If that ally is @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.MZ8OoH1GE9qDMyCD]{Flat-Footed} or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.yUtkoIshf4dPruNd]{off-target}, you end that condition. If circumstances would cause the ally to immediately become Flat-Footed or off-target again, you instead suppress that condition for 1 round.</p>"
